31:13.117 --> 31:15.665
to Miss Carter for years
prior to Mr. Roy's death.

31:15.665 --> 31:18.127
- She was a friend
of the defendant.

31:22.344 --> 31:24.098
We believe that Michelle Carter

31:24.098 --> 31:26.185
may have orchestrated
Conrad's death

31:26.185 --> 31:29.441
in order to get the attention
and sympathy of Susie Pierce.

31:31.112 --> 31:32.740
- Who is Dr. Peter Breggin?

31:32.740 --> 31:34.034
Oh, he's
a psychologist.

31:34.034 --> 31:35.705
He submitted a full report
on the mental health

31:35.705 --> 31:37.625
of Michelle Carter
and Conrad Roy III.

31:37.625 --> 31:39.504
- Are these police officers
from the crime scene?

31:39.504 --> 31:40.881
- No, no, no, they'll speak

31:40.881 --> 31:42.802
to reports
of the sustained domestic abuse

31:42.802 --> 31:44.179
experienced inside
the household

31:44.179 --> 31:46.225
which could have influenced
the young man's death.

31:46.225 --> 31:49.273
- These officers and EMTs
were not present on the night

31:49.273 --> 31:51.360
of the incident
with Conrad Roy Jr.

31:51.360 --> 31:53.239
and Conrad Roy III.

31:53.239 --> 31:55.493
The hearsay rule
forbids them

31:55.493 --> 31:57.247
from being admitted
into evidence.

31:57.247 --> 31:59.126
So none--none of them
were there?

31:59.126 --> 32:01.005
- One of them was,
Officer Tavares.

32:01.005 --> 32:02.382
- Then why are the rest
of these officers

32:02.382 --> 32:03.594
on the witness list?

32:03.594 --> 32:05.388
- Oh, well,
because Mr. Cataldo plans

32:05.388 --> 32:07.852
to raise issues that happened
well before the victim's death

32:07.852 --> 32:10.691
in order to raise suspicion
about a home life that was,

32:10.691 --> 32:13.655
except this incident,
loving and attentive.

32:13.655 --> 32:15.075
- But some girl that my client

32:15.075 --> 32:17.496
hasn't spoken to in two years
is somehow the--

32:17.496 --> 32:19.166
Okay, whoa, whoa.
Hold on, hold on.

32:19.166 --> 32:21.087
Here's what we're gonna do.

32:21.087 --> 32:23.174
Officer Tavares is admitted.

32:23.174 --> 32:26.472
Susie Pierce and the other
officers and EMTs are not.

32:26.472 --> 32:27.767
And we're gonna limit
the scope

32:27.767 --> 32:29.103
