Let me finish.

32:32.234 --> 32:34.154
We're gonna limit the scope
of the investigation

32:34.154 --> 32:36.868
to 18 months
prior to Mr. Roy's passing.

32:36.868 --> 32:38.246
- Judge, 18 months--
- Your Honor, I would like--

32:38.246 --> 32:39.414
That's--that's--
that's my ruling.

32:39.414 --> 32:40.960
That's my ruling.

32:40.960 --> 32:44.007
Thank you.
