Interview with Carter's mother,
her neighbor,

32:54.863 --> 32:56.365
her softball coach.

32:56.365 --> 32:57.994
- Not her friends?
- No, it seems not.

32:57.994 --> 33:00.331
- Great, okay, well,
you know, we just--we--

33:00.331 --> 33:01.793
we roll with the punches.

33:01.793 --> 33:03.337
We take what we have,
and we just roll with them.

33:03.337 --> 33:04.591
